 P[ (X -1) / 2 £ (5.21  -1) / 
 2]  = P(Z £ 2.105) » P(Z £ 2.11) = .4826 + .5 = .9826
 Notice that P(Z £ 0) = .5
 Similarly, P(X ? 2.1) = P(Z ? 
(2.1 -  1) / (2)) = P(Z ? .55) =  0.5 - .2088 = .2912

